    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The cloying scent of poppies lulls your foes into slumber, heedless of the vines creeping in. Make an attack. If it hits, the target gains [sprout 2] and becomes sickened for two rounds. While they are sickened by this effect, they cannot take actions outside of their turn and must cast defensively as they see phantoms in the corners of their eyes. The creature may tear off blooms to end the sickened effect early.</p>"
